EAN.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;《巫师：深海塞壬》。&lt;/em>; |图片：Netflix&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;《阿凡达：最后的气宗》、《斯科特朝圣者起飞》、《鬼泣》、《怪奇物语》和《3 Body Problem》都在 Netflix 的 Geeked 2023 展示会上放映。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23948622/netflix-geeked-week-2023-stranger-things-5-avatar-last-airbender-3-body-problem&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip; &lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23948622/netflix-geeked-week-2023-stranger-things-5-avatar-last-airbender-3-body-problem" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23948622/netflix-geeked-week-2023-stranger-things-5-avatar-last-airbender-3-body-problem</id><author><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name><name>阿什·帕里什</name><name>查尔斯·普利亚姆-摩尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-11T13:24:17-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-11T13:24:17-05:00</updated><title>演员工会的罢工协议已进入最后一步</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;双色调紫色背景上的 SAG-AFTRA 徽标。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HI-nveCZrFEYNIzOEKVW9r5mbd8=/0x0:3001x2001/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72855271/STK159_SAG_AFTRA_03.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插画：William Joel / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;irGFI8&quot;>;美国演员工会-美国电视和广播艺术家联合会 (SAG-AFTRA) &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/8/23945647/hollywood-actors-sag-aftra-strike-contract-deal&quot;>;与好莱坞制片厂高管达成暂定协议&lt;/a>;，有效结束了&lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/7/17/23798246/strike-hollywoods-writers-actors-wga-sag-aftra&quot;>;为期 118 天的演员罢工&lt;/a>;。昨天，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.sagaftra.org/sag-aftra-national-board-approves-tentative-agreement-recommends-ratification-2023-tvtheatrical&quot;>;SAG-AFTRA 宣布&lt;/a>;国家委员会已以 86% 比 14% 的投票结果批准了该协议，并建议工会成员投票批准。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ChKrXG&quot;>;该协议在技术上仍处于等待状态，直到 12 月 5 日统计工会成员的投票结果为止。 ，尽管该协会表示其一些功能将在批准过程中生效，例如某些加薪。 SAG-AFTRA 在其公告中提供了交易摘要：&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;ukrpZS&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component= &quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;好莱坞演员仍在罢工&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/7 /17/23798246/strike-hollywoods-writers-actors-wga-sag-aftra&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;ul>; &lt;li id=&quot;JrsQ1T&quot;>; &lt;strong>;流媒体收入：流媒体节目的收入&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/7/14/23795311/hollywood-strike-wga-sag-aftra-streaming&quot;>;巨大公会战斗的一部分。公会称其“实现了……&lt;/li>; &lt;/ul>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/11/23956660/sag-aftra-actors-strike -deal-approved-streaming-revenue-ai&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/11/23956660/sag-aftra-actors-strike-deal-approved-streaming-revenue-ai" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/11/23956660/sag-aftra-actors-strike-deal-approved-streaming-revenue-ai</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-11T10:15:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-11T10:15:00-05:00</updated><title>咄咄逼人的结帐屏幕正在助长“通货膨胀”</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Panera 提示屏幕&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/yjylaqdA8hAlNrgqvVtHIRhn1ac=/0x0:4032x2688/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads /chorus_image/image/72854827/IMG_2659.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Panera 的小费提示稍好一些，因为您可以选择美元金额，并且有披露称您的小费“可能”会分发给符合条件的员工.&lt;/em>; |摄影：Victoria Song / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;UGQBnU&quot;>;给小费是美国一项古老的争论。您支付多少钱以及何时支付？这是一种选择还是一种义务？总的来说，多年来，科技至少让一切变得更容易。智能手机让朋友们可以轻而易举地拿出计算器来算出小费并分摊账单。现在，从实体商店到送货应用程序，各地的结账屏幕都添加了旨在让您更轻松地支付小费的按钮。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;LS6hQN&quot;>;这很方便，但事实并非如此。根据皮尤研究中心的一份新&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.pewresearch.org/2023/11/09/tipping-culture-in-america-public-sees-a-changed-landscape/&quot;>;报告&lt; /a>;，美国的小费文化近年来发生了转变。百分之七十二的美国人表示，与五年前相比，更多的地方需要给小费。并非所有这些都与技术相关，但很难否认&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cbsnews.com/news/tipping-culture-etiquette-evolving-with-gratuity-screens-everywhere/#:~ :text=技术%20has%20played%20a%20large%20role%20in%20change%20the%20rules%20around%20tipping.%20Touch%20screens%20with%20tip%20prompts%20are%20increasing%20replacing%20old%2Dfashioned%20tip% 20jars%2C%20which%20were%20easier%20to%20slip%20past%20and%20ignore.%20And%20on%20a%20screen%2C%20you%20have%20to%20actively%20reject%20the%20request.%C2%A0&quot; >;结帐屏幕在小费膨胀中的作用&lt;/a>;。甚至...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/11/23955381/checkout-screens-tipping-pos-kiosk&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/一个>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/11/23955381/checkout-screens-tipping-pos-kiosk" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/11/23955381/checkout-screens-tipping-pos-kiosk</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry></feed>